November 17, 1994, Thursday, Southland Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 1; Column 3; Sports Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
