<DOCNO> LA111794-0058 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 099309 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
November 17, 1994, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
