14.3 Arthur C. Brown* 4,353 12.0 Larry T. Wieck 4,343 12.0 Wiley S. Drake 4,145 
11.5 Marilyn Kietzman 3,851 10.7 Lawrence J. Barstow 3,839 10.6 Les McAdams 
2,227 6.2 *** 
</P>
<P>
