 Short film and video work in all genres will be presented, many with their 
makers present.The festival premiered in Bozeman, Mont., at the University Film 
and Video Assn.; Los Angeles is the third stop in the program's North American 
tour. The association, which includes teachers, students and others interested 
in the development of film as a means of communication, was founded in 1947. 
