<P>
MARLA GIBBS THEATRE TO HAVE JAZZ EVENING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Another Evening of Jazz," featuring Charles Owens, will be presented at 8:30 
p.m. Friday at Marla Gibbs' Vision Theatre, Los Angeles. 
</P>
<P>
 Tax-deductible tickets are $20 in advance, $22 at the door or $50 for 
preferred seating and patron listing. 
</P>
<P>
 Proceeds will benefit the Los Angeles Chapter of the Prairie View A&M 
University Scholarship program. For tickets or information, call (213) 755-3147 
or (213) 291-1976. 
