Penn State 9-0 2 Nebraska 11-0 3 Alabama 10-0 4 Miami 8-1 5 Auburn 9-0-1 6 
Colorado 9-1 7 Florida 8-1 8 Florida State 8-1 9 Kansas State 7-2 10 Oregon 8-3 
