<P>
 Anybody scouting the Bruins on Wednesday would have had trouble recognizing 
the players. For instance, J.J. Stokes wore the No. 85 of Jim McElroy. . . . 
Running back Sharmon Shah missed Wednesday's practice because of flu. JIM 
HODGES 
